parameters:
\nc<Senpai>"It seems they really took a liking to you, Saki. They even
left a tip."
\bustMsgExp[2, 2]\nc<Senpai>"This is my share for recommending you."
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>"Ahhh! Taking even the tip is just too cruel!"
\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>"Sorry, maybe that joke went a bit too far."

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>"But you shouldn't talk about the tip with others. Other
managers would take it without any hesitation..."

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>"If you look at our company, you should be able to tell that
much."

\nc<Senpai>"Well then, let's clean up quickly. I'll be entrusting the
VIP hospitality to you from now on."
